"{\"uid\": \"outsideonline.com-outdoor-adventure-olympics-paris-olympics-tv\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"We can not wait to watch the Olympics on TV or streaming(Photo: Clive Rose / Getty Images) The2024 Summer Olympics in Parisofficially kick off this Friday, July 26, with the opening ceremonies in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999772626, \"rank\": 2.283786085371587e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 25, \"to\": 37}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 43}, {\"ngram\": \"Clive Rose / Getty Images\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 89}, {\"ngram\": \"The2024\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 98}, {\"ngram\": \"Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 99, \"to\": 114}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisofficially\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 133}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Across the country, millions of Americans-myself included-are preparing to glue ourselves to the television to watch every javelin throw, ping pong smash, and tear of joy or disappointment between now and the closing ceremonies on August 11.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"Americans\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"the television\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"every javelin throw\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"ping pong smash\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 358}, {\"ngram\": \"tear\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 375}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointment\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"now and the closing ceremonies\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But oh, what a dizzying amount of events to watch!\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"But oh, what a dizzying amount\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the Paris Games, there will be 39 sports to follow and 329 different competitions to watch-that equates to approximately 7,000 hours of live coverage across 17 days.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"39 sports\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"329 different competitions\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"approximately 7,000 hours\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"live coverage\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"17 days\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every single event will be televised in some way by the the Olympics' American broadcaster, NBC, which will show a glut of coverage across network TV, cable channels and online streaming.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.1122456432098986e-12, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.6436838214455651, \"rank\": 0.5535577174602464, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every single event\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"some way\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"a glut\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"coverage\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 809}, {\"ngram\": \"network TV\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"cable channels\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"online streaming\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Catching every minute of the action is a tall order, even for the most diehard Olympics aficionado.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every minute\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"a tall order\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"the most diehard Olympics aficionado\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, to help you figure out your viewing strategy, I have created a helpful guide below.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your viewing strategy\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"a helpful guide\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are an Olympics diehard who wants to have live access to each and every single sport, you are going to have to stream the action online.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"live access\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"every single sport\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are two ways to do this.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two ways\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you already pay for a cable TV subscription, you can login to NBCOlympics.com or NBC.com (or download the NBC app or the NBC Olympics app) with your account information and simply stream via your web browser, or via your phone, tablet, or connected TV.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC.com\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.6436838214455651, \"rank\": 0.5535577174602464, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cable TV subscription\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"NBCOlympics.com\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"the NBC Olympics app\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"your account information\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"your web browser\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"your phone\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"tablet\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"connected TV\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not have a cable TV subscription, you will need to download thePeacock app.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cable TV subscription\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"thePeacock app\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's also your cheapest option-the monthly plan starts at $7.99, or you can update to $13.99if you do not want to see advertisements.\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your cheapest option\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"the monthly plan\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"advertisements\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The annual plan gives you greater savings.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The annual plan\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"greater savings\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those of us who follow the Tour de France already know and love the app.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1778, \"end\": 1792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999969230631949, \"rank\": 3.0618510836660084e-06, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"the app\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock will beam 5,000 hours of Olympics coverage.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peacock\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"5,000 hours\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics coverage\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yep, that equates to every single Olympic live event, and it will also allow you to watch replays of competitions after they have happened.\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yep\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"every single Olympic live event\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"replays\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1974}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be curated highlight videos, plus three different studio shows.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"highlight videos\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2055}, {\"ngram\": \"three different studio shows\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One program, calledOlympic Highlights with Kevin Hart & Kenan Thompson,will blend comedy and recaps.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2148, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenan_Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenan Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenan_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenan_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One program\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"calledOlympic Highlights\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"Kevin Hart\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"comedy\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"recaps\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The other,Gold Zone,is described by NBC's PR department as a \\\"whip-around show that guides viewers to the best and most exciting live moments throughout the games.\\\"\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2229, \"end\": 2232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.6436838214455651, \"rank\": 0.5535577174602464, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2235, \"end\": 2237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_relations\", \"score\": 0.9995562675300153, \"rank\": 0.0004439242892562278, \"text\": \"PR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_relations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_relations\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The other,Gold Zone\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"whip-around show\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"the best and most exciting live moments\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2334}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The final show,Watch with Alex Cooper,is hosted by host of the popular podcast,Call Her Daddy, who will offer her own take on the action.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2384, \"end\": 2395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\", \"score\": 0.8607573575018954, \"rank\": 0.16176470588237404, \"text\": \"Alex Cooper\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The final show\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"host\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"the popular podcast\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"Her Daddy\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"her own take\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Long story short: If you are the hardest of hardcore Olympics fans, Peacock is your best bet.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hardcore Olympics fans\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2563}, {\"ngram\": \"Peacock\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"your best bet\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If streaming is not your jam, you can still watch an abundance of live Olympics coverage on TV and cable-but you are going to have to wake up early.\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2740, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"streaming\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"your jam\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"an abundance\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"live Olympics coverage\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2686}, {\"ngram\": \"cable\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since Paris is six hours ahead of the United States' Eastern time zone, the television coverage for live events will kick off in the mornings